        "description": "Nonlinear elastic-plastic material model (bilinear isotropic hardening, Ti-6Al-4V properties per ASTM F136) selected based on published material characterization data. Frictional contact (μ=0.2) at screw-rod interface. Model form choices documented and justified in the modeling report. Gradation 3 achieved: model form selected from literature-supported alternatives with documented justification."
