      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening model is well-established for Ti-6Al-4V under monotonic quasi-static loading. Contact formulation (augmented Lagrange, μ=0.2) is consistent with published tribological data for titanium-on-titanium interfaces. Alternative model forms (kinematic hardening, Chaboche) were considered and rejected as unnecessary for monotonic loading."
