        "description": "Quantitative comparison using E/uval metric (validation uncertainty normalized error). Acceptance bound: |E/uval| < 1.96 for all three QoIs. Additional check: percent difference < 10%. Statistical comparison accounts for experimental variability (CV across N=11) and model input uncertainty (Monte Carlo). Gradation 4 achieved: uncertainty-normalized comparison with documented statistical framework."
