      },
      "rationale": "Stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm are the three primary ASTM F1717 metrics used in FDA 510(k) submissions for pedicle screw systems. Direct linkage to clinical failure modes documented in the design risk analysis (FMEA reference: DePuy-FMEA-2023-PS75)."
